  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK449">
<l>mutalilārk kūtiya millai matalaiyāñ</l>
<l>cārpilārk killai nilai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There can be no gain to those who have no capital and in like manner there can be no permanence to those who are without the support of adherents.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
